      "review_summary": "The PR changes Claude live `can_use_tool` allow responses and Codex native `PermissionRequest` relay allow responses to include the requested tool input in `updatedInput`, with updated assertions.\n\nPR surface: Source +5, Tests +34. Total +39 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level for the PR-introduced defect: Codex source rejects PermissionRequest `decision.updatedInput`, and this PR adds that field to Codex native-hook allow responses. I did not run a live Claude Code or Codex session in this read-only review.",
